OL,3,CSpring surge: UK temperatures set to
OL,4,Csoar ` but how warm could it get?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHow long will the warmer spell last?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773667695
OL,3,CSpring surge: UK temperatures set to
OL,4,Csoar ` but how warm could it get?
OL,6,FAfter a chilly and unsettled start to
OL,7,Fthe week, high pressure should start
OL,8,Fto build in from the east throughout
OL,9,FTuesday, with the decent conditions
OL,10,Fexpected to spread to much of the UK
OL,11,Fthrough midweek, lasting at least
OL,12,Funtil the end of the week. Some
OL,13,Findications actually suggest that area
OL,14,Fof high pressure will dominate for the
OL,15,Frest of the month, but it's too early
OL,16,Fto give much detail yet.
OL,18,FIs that it for cold weather now?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773667695
OL,3,CSpring surge: UK temperatures set to
OL,4,Csoar ` but how warm could it get?
OL,6,FNo - early spring can still bring
OL,7,Fsharp swings in temperature, so cooler
OL,8,Fspells aren't completely out of the
OL,9,Fquestion yet, although cold snaps
OL,10,Fgenerally become less frequent as we
OL,11,Fmove further into the season. With
OL,12,Flonger daylight hours and stronger
OL,13,Fsunshine at this time of year,
OL,14,Ftemperatures can rise surprisingly
OL,15,Fquickly when skies are clear.
OL,17,FFor now though, during times that can
OL,18,Ffeel like good news is in short
OL,19,Fsupply, we can all look forward to
OL,20,Fsome beautiful weather that will both
OL,21,Fwarm the ground and raise the spirits!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
